headline.main: Later from Havana.; ARRIVAL OF THE BLACK WARRIOR.

docs.lead_paragraph: The United State Mall steamship Black Warrior. J. W. SMITH Commander, from New-Orleans 12th, and Havana the 15th inst., arrived at this port early yesterday morning. Part of the Spanish fleet, viz: 1 frigate, 1 ship-of-the-line, I sloop I brig, and 1 steam frigate, sailed from Havana on the 12th inst., for a cruise in the Gulf, for the health of the crews,

docs.lead_paragraph: Monsieur Blondel, whose appointment as Belgian Minister to the United States is announced, is the gentleman who represented Belgium at the Court of the Sultan from the Spring of 1849 to the Summer of last year, when, owing to his alleged undue Interference in the Danubian Principalities question, his recall was requested by the Turkish Government.

docs.lead_paragraph: The little town of Dracut, Mass., is supping on horrors. A few days ago there was a horrible case of parricide there. On Thursday last, a young man of 26m JONATHAN HOLLOWELL, cut his throat at his father's house. The cause is supposed to have been depression of spirits, caused by ill health. HALLOWELL had a wife in Rhode Island.

docs.lead_paragraph: The Royal Mail steamship America, Capt. LOTT, from Liverpool 10 1/2 o'clock on the morning of the 2d instant, arrived here at 10 o'clock this (Saturday) morning, Her dates are three days later than those received by the North American at Portland. Among the passengers by the America are Madame LOLA MONTEZ, Countess of LANDSFELDT, (who was recently married to the Prince SHALOSKY in Paris,) and suite;
